-- Russia cbank will lower rates when sure of 4 pct medium-term inflation
-- 
-- Fri May 23, 2014 04:24AM EDT
-- None



St Petersburg, May 23 (Reuters) - Russia's central bank will lower interest rates when it is sure of meeting its 4 percent target for medium-term inflation, the bank's governor Elvira Nabiullina said at the St Petersburg International Economic Forum on Friday.

